nodes.text: Cyn Jodu was a female Nagai lieutenant in the Nagai expeditionary force.

Alongside her superior officer, Commander Dal Zorfenn, Jodu was tasked with securing the planet Kinooine that it might serve as the primary base of operations for the Nagai fleet's planned invasion of the galaxy.
The character was named for comic book artist Cynthia Martin and writer Jo Duffy.
